OL,3,CParents warned after 'man in black
OL,4,Ccar' follows schoolgirls
OL,6,FParents have been warned after two
OL,7,Fschoolgirls reported being followed by
OL,8,Fa man while on their way to school.
OL,10,FThe man, dressed in a black tracksuit,
OL,11,Fapproached the pupils in Crosby,
OL,12,FMerseyside, and followed them until a
OL,13,Fwoman walking her dog intervened and
OL,14,Fescorted the girls safely to school.
OL,16,FFollowing the incident, on 21 October,
OL,17,Fan email was sent from Sefton Council
OL,18,Fto all Crosby schools, who then
OL,19,Falerted parents.
