OL,6,FThe message, seen by the Local
OL,7,FDemocracy Reporting Service, and
OL,8,Fconfirmed by Sefton Council, gave
OL,9,Fdetails of the incident, which
OL,10,Fallegedly occurred at the corner of
OL,11,FNorthern Road and Trevor Drive.
OL,13,FThe email was titled: 'Safeguarding
OL,14,FAlert' and said: "On the way to school
OL,15,Fthis morning, (two children) have
OL,16,Freported being followed by a man.
