OL,3,CParents warned after 'man in black
OL,4,Ccar' follows schoolgirls
OL,6,F"They say that he ran toward them and
OL,7,Fthen power-walked when they turned to
OL,8,Flook at him. They power-walked and hid
OL,9,Fbehind a wall (the entrance to the
OL,10,Fpark on Trevor Drive).
OL,12,F"He ran back to his car and drove
OL,13,Fslowly along Trevor Drive. By this
OL,14,Ftime a woman walking a dog took the
OL,15,F(children) toward school until they
OL,16,Ffelt safe."
OL,18,FThe man is described as being in his
OL,19,F40s, white, bald on top with hair
OL,20,Faround and approximately 5ft 10in tall.
