OL,6,FHe was also seen driving a black car
OL,7,Fwith tinted windows and was said to be
OL,8,Fwearing a black tracksuit and put on a
OL,9,Fblack bucket hat.
OL,11,FFollowing the incident Merseyside
OL,12,FPolice said there was "no indication a
OL,13,Fcrime took place or that a crime was
OL,14,Fattempted".
OL,16,FA spokesperson for the force said: "We
OL,17,Fcan confirm we received a report of
OL,18,Falleged suspicious behaviour in Crosby
OL,19,Fthis morning, Monday 21 October.
