OL,6,F"At around 8.10am it was alleged that
OL,7,Fa man was acting suspiciously on
OL,8,FNorthern Road as two schoolgirls were
OL,9,Fwalking to school.
OL,11,F"There is no indication a crime took
OL,12,Fplace or that a crime was attempted.
OL,14,F"Officers from Sefton Local Policing
OL,15,Fteam are patrolling the area and are
OL,16,Fliaising with the local schools.
OL,18,F"Enquiries are ongoing.
